title: Kamp van Koningsbrugge
overview: Jeroen van Koningsbrugge faces an enormous challenge ... Find fifteen ordinary citizens who think they are mentally and physically strong enough to handle one of the toughest courses in the Netherlands: The Special Forces training. Van Koningsbrugge supplies his people to a team of highly experienced specialists who will take care of the recruits. A unique experiment in which the utmost is demanded ... and van Koningsbrugge is there to support his men and women ...
